room_title: Escape room "Locker Room Lockdown" by Escape Room Wisconsin in Green Bay
room_description: He was one of the most successful coaches in professional football history. Legends say that he has kept his book of winning plays locked within his office, which is still housed at the hallowed grounds of Lambeau field. Upon entering the office, you find that the new security system has locked you in and you have only 60 minutes to find the playbook and escape before the championship game begins! Can you do it?
